txt.en: Those most loyal to Ivar have been granted exceptional protections. A true hero will tackle this adversity, not avoid it.
Do not remove any corruptions from Ivar's Champions
Ivar is waiting deep within Ost Dunhoth.
Ivar's champions draw power from dark corruptions. To show the Gaunt-lord that you fear no evil power, defeat Ivar and his champions without removing any corruptions.
